"5  small red, gold, and Chioggia beets (about 1 1/2 lb.)","1 tablespoon water","1  frozen puff pastry sheet, thawed","1 tablespoon fresh orange juice","1 1/2 teaspoons honey","1 1/2 tablespoons chopped hazelnuts, toasted","1 1/2 teaspoons fresh thyme leaves","1/2 teaspoon flaked sea salt (such as Maldon)","1 1/2 ounces goat cheese, crumbled (about 1/3 cup)"